&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The AI Transformation Manager reports to the Chief Data and AI Officer and plays a critical role in driving Cross River’s AI-led transformation and commercialization strategy. This position is responsible for orchestrating the end-to-end implementation of AI initiatives across the enterprise—bridging strategy, productization, compliance, and delivery to ensure measurable business impact. The ideal candidate combines deep expertise in AI/ML program management with a pragmatic understanding of financial services and regulatory environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Strategy &amp;amp; Governance&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and manage the AI Transformation roadmap, ensuring alignment with Cross River’s strategic objectives, regulatory standards, and innovation priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with business, data, and technology leaders to identify AI-driven opportunities for efficiency, risk management, and new revenue models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish a governance framework for AI projects, including evaluation metrics, responsible AI principles, and lifecycle management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee commercialization of AI capabilities, enabling scalable deployment of internal tools and potential external monetization opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Program Execution &amp;amp; Delivery&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the planning, coordination, and execution of AI initiatives across multiple business domains—banking, lending, risk, compliance, and customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain a portfolio management system for all AI programs, ensuring transparency on timelines, costs, dependencies, and outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data readiness and model governance across all AI deployments in close partnership with data engineering and compliance teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report on transformation metrics, including adoption, ROI, and productivity gains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
