&lt;li&gt;Work hands-on with large loan-level datasets using Python and SQL to build analytical frameworks that evaluate collateral performance, identify risk concentrations, and inform assumption-setting across the portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain detailed cash flow models to project expected returns, losses, and structural outcomes under base, upside, and stress scenarios&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate deal structures, waterfall mechanics, triggers, credit enhancement levels, and subordination to assess current and projected credit risk&lt;/li&gt;
