&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Valuation Allowance&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the team&#39;s primary liaison to Valuation/Risk/Accounting teams during the quarterly valuation allowance process&lt;/li&gt;
